1
00:00:06,100 --> 00:00:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess that's the last day 
of middle school.</font>

2
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}56TH GRADUATION CEREMONY
NISHI SHINJU MIDDLE SCHOOL</font>

3
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There wasn't anything 
particularly interesting about it.</font>

4
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't really feel anything.</font>

5
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miku-senpai, please 
come hang out sometime.</font>

6
00:00:17,830 --> 00:00:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, yup.</font>

7
00:00:19,150 --> 00:00:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looks like it's different for her.</i></font>

8
00:00:22,030 --> 00:00:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She keeps moving ahead 
in life without me.</i></font>

9
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I bet she's the most popular 
girl in school already.</i></font>

10
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not that I really know.</i></font>

11
00:00:30,140 --> 00:00:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just how many people 
are getting drawn to her?</i></font>

12
00:00:34,740 --> 00:00:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all sign our graduation albums.</font>

13
00:00:35,180 --> 00:00:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}GRADUATION</font>

14
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to head home.</font>

15
00:00:42,930 --> 00:00:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why would anyone scribble in something 
as precious as a graduation album, anyway?</i></font>

16
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Way better to keep it clean.</i></font>

17
00:00:52,370 --> 00:00:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya!</font>

18
00:01:00,260 --> 00:01:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened?</font>

19
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean, "What happened"?!</font>

20
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the last time we're 
taking this road in this uniform.</font>

21
00:01:10,540 --> 00:01:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to spend 
the last walk home with you.</font>

22
00:01:16,340 --> 00:01:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did that get you?</font>

23
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, show me your graduation album.</font>

24
00:01:21,190 --> 00:01:22,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just give it!</font>

25
00:01:22,290 --> 00:01:23,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

26
00:01:25,290 --> 00:01:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?!</font>

27
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

28
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}- TRY TO BE MORE HONEST.
- KNOCK BEFORE YOU ENTER WAKANA'S ROOM 
- FIX YOUR BEDHEAD BEFORE SCHOOL</font>

29
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DON'T BE STUCK UP IN HIGH SCHOOL. MAKE FRIENDS</font>

30
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:39,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LOOK PEOPLE IN THE EYE
WHEN YOU TALK TO THEM</font>

31
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's just roasting the hell out of me!</i></font>

32
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good for you.</font>

33
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must have felt lonely, 
having no one write in your album.</font>

34
00:01:46,050 --> 00:01:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never asked for this.</font>

35
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to end school with a slate
 as clean as the driven snow.</font>

36
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, sure.</font>

37
00:01:52,910 --> 00:01:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't have to 
chase me down just to...</font>

38
00:01:57,600 --> 00:02:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, of course.</i></font>

39
00:02:00,490 --> 00:02:03,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She chased me down just for this.</i></font>

40
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How can she even write so fast 
in such a short time?</i></font>

41
00:02:08,570 --> 00:02:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's right, too.</i></font>

42
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm such a loser.</i></font>

43
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's always by my side like this...</i></font>

44
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:24,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't stay like this forever.</i></font>

45
00:02:25,090 --> 00:02:27,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wanna go by Uncle's?</font>

46
00:02:27,350 --> 00:02:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He might treat us to cake 
for our graduation.</font>

47
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

48
00:02:32,050 --> 00:02:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to catch up 
when I'm in high school!</font>

49
00:02:42,110 --> 00:02:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Caught you blushing!</font>

50
00:02:43,610 --> 00:02:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you!</font>

51
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 3: CHILDHOOD FRIEND SEDUCTION</font>

52
00:03:05,790 --> 00:03:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Nacchan and I were saying 
we should go for a yummy lunch.</font>

53
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya, do you know any good places?</font>

54
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fujiya Udon's pretty good, no?</font>

55
00:03:16,650 --> 00:03:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also your uncle's omurice.</font>

56
00:03:19,970 --> 00:03:21,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those are good, but...</i></font>

57
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been to Uncle's so many times.</i></font>

58
00:03:24,690 --> 00:03:25,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm bored.</i></font>

59
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:28,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to go somewhere new and cute.</i></font>

60
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh?</font>

61
00:03:38,850 --> 00:03:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, I gotta go.</i></font>

62
00:03:41,370 --> 00:03:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, o-okay.</font>

63
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's wrong?</i></font>

64
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You sound so sad.</i></font>

65
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dummy.</font>

66
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Bye.</i></font>

67
00:03:51,450 --> 00:03:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A little early, but good night.</i></font>

68
00:03:57,250 --> 00:04:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Miku has lots of friends 
both online and in IRL.</i></font>

69
00:04:00,850 --> 00:04:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She must have promised 
a call or something.</i></font>

70
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}#MIKU'S ROOM - OFFLINE: 4
MIKU - REIJI - YUKIYA - NATSUKI</font>

71
00:04:05,650 --> 00:04:08,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never knew there was apple pie flavor.</font>

72
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want half?</font>

73
00:04:09,770 --> 00:04:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay.</font>

74
00:04:10,810 --> 00:04:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}KOI-KYUN</font>

75
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I wish we could be this way forever.</i></font>

76
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Talking with you makes my 
heart race, Takanashi-kun.</i></font>

77
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe, if I were like this guy,</i></font>

78
00:04:25,810 --> 00:04:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could have gotten more 
out of that conversation earlier.</i></font>

79
00:04:30,290 --> 00:04:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It isn't guaranteed that she's 
going to stick around forever.</i></font>

80
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no telling how her feelings 
are going to change going forward.</i></font>

81
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's where you're at, huh?</font>

82
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}HANABA HINAKO - THIRD YEAR UNIVERSITY
WORKS AT KANADE CAFE</font>

83
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're living your youth, Yukki.</font>

84
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oi.</font>

85
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So where is my beloved Miku?</font>

86
00:04:51,490 --> 00:04:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She left. She said 
she had something to do.</font>

87
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SHINONOME MASARU - MIKU'S UNCLE
OWNER OF CAFE KANADE</font>

88
00:04:56,470 --> 00:04:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done.</font>

89
00:04:58,010 --> 00:04:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to work anymore.</font>

90
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hinako-kun, time to close.</font>

91
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want my hours, so nope.</font>

92
00:05:05,590 --> 00:05:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What could a guy do to 
make you happy, Hinako-san?</font>

93
00:05:10,290 --> 00:05:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Money.</font>

94
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that even a valid answer 
to my question?</font>

95
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">High-quality bags, high-quality 
cosmetics, high-quality necklaces.</font>

96
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like it most when 
a guy spends money on me.</font>

97
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE RELATIONSHIP ENDS
WHEN THE MONEY ENDS</font>

98
00:05:23,890 --> 00:05:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so brass tacks.</font>

99
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cold.</font>

100
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cold, huh?</font>

101
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so young, Yukki.</font>

102
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, all sorts of costs go 
into enjoying expensive things.</font>

103
00:05:37,970 --> 00:05:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Costs?</font>

104
00:05:39,170 --> 00:05:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In most cases, you'll get something decent</font>

105
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if you just buy something online 
with decent reviews.</font>

106
00:05:44,470 --> 00:05:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you want something that'll 
earn the most appreciation,</font>

107
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's not just the price tag 
of high-quality products.</font>

108
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The time it takes to choose, 
to do research, to go to the store...</font>

109
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's all sorts of costs involved.</font>

110
00:05:58,450 --> 00:06:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you put some extra thought into it</font>

111
00:06:00,730 --> 00:06:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when you're buying something 
a little nicer than usual?</font>

112
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did have to think pretty hard 
when I bought my PC.</font>

113
00:06:06,730 --> 00:06:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't want to mess it up, after all.</font>

114
00:06:08,810 --> 00:06:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly. That's what I mean.</font>

115
00:06:11,230 --> 00:06:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The question is, can you do 
the same thing for your special someone?</font>

116
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more time and money you spend on it,</font>

117
00:06:18,150 --> 00:06:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the more it comes across that you 
put in an effort to make them happy.</font>

118
00:06:23,990 --> 00:06:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most people can see that.</font>

119
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:30,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The best way to make someone happy 
is to pay those costs, I think.</font>

120
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're surprisingly thoughtful 
about these things.</font>

121
00:06:35,490 --> 00:06:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you fallen for me?</font>

122
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:39,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're welcome to try again 
when you can earn your own money.</font>

123
00:06:39,730 --> 00:06:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I definitely wouldn't 
spend anything on you.</font>

124
00:06:43,410 --> 00:06:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, though.</font>

125
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Costs, huh?</i></font>

126
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I did spend a lot 
for my high school debut...</i></font>

127
00:06:54,590 --> 00:06:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay.</i></font>

128
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:04,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MOM
INCOMING CALL</font>

129
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom?</font>

130
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm making it now.</font>

131
00:07:08,990 --> 00:07:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are, huh?</font>

132
00:07:11,020 --> 00:07:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's fine.</font>

133
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll keep it in the fridge.</font>

134
00:07:14,250 --> 00:07:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be sure to eat it when you get home.</font>

135
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:18,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, good luck.</font>

136
00:07:22,710 --> 00:07:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}YUKIYA
INCOMING CALL</font>

137
00:07:26,970 --> 00:07:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

138
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

139
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, y'know...</i></font>

140
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, I was just thinking,</i></font>

141
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>you must have chosen somewhere half-assed 
for your lunch with Nacchan-san.</i></font>

142
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd just check 
on Meshi Log before I go.</font>

143
00:07:41,860 --> 00:07:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ugh, you normies...</i></font>

144
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let me guess, when you 
say "somewhere cute,"</i></font>

145
00:07:46,650 --> 00:07:48,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>you mean somewhere grammable, don't you?</i></font>

146
00:07:48,910 --> 00:07:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You know, the word "photogenic" overseas 
is only used to described people.</i></font>

147
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In other words, it isn't 
just what you're eating</i></font>

148
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but the synergy between 
the people eating and the food</i></font>

149
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that contributes the
 photogenicness to the synergy.</i></font>

150
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd appreciate if you didn't talk 
about grammableness so casually</i></font>

151
00:08:01,230 --> 00:08:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>without even understanding what it means.</i></font>

152
00:08:03,550 --> 00:08:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your point?</font>

153
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll show you how it's done.</i></font>

154
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sunday, 9 o'clock, at the station.</i></font>

155
00:08:09,410 --> 00:08:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Bye.</i></font>

156
00:08:10,210 --> 00:08:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

157
00:08:11,350 --> 00:08:13,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What?</font>

158
00:08:13,410 --> 00:08:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

159
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? What? What?</font>

160
00:08:17,730 --> 00:08:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

161
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no turning back now.</i></font>

162
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}#2: NISHIMAI AMUSEMENT PARK
A CLASSIC DATE VENUE!</font>

163
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Amusement parks, aquariums...</i></font>

164
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've already been to all of them with 
Miku with family or on field trips.</i></font>

165
00:08:35,790 --> 00:08:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TOP 10 DATING DESTINATIONS FOR COUPLES
FROM THE COMMON TO THE BEST-KEPT SECRETS</font>

166
00:08:35,790 --> 00:08:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She already goes to fancy places that 
I wouldn't even know about all the time.</i></font>

167
00:08:43,210 --> 00:08:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to put in the "cost" 
that Hinako-san talks about</i></font>

168
00:08:46,190 --> 00:08:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and make it a date 
that Miku will never forget!</i></font>

169
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We've been playing the love game 
pretty aggressively lately...</i></font>

170
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This has to be a date, right?</i></font>

171
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He makes it so obvious!</i></font>

172
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't remember the last time 
I went out with Yukiya.</i></font>

173
00:09:08,190 --> 00:09:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We used to go to the food court a lot.</i></font>

174
00:09:11,330 --> 00:09:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yukiya's so stingy,
sometimes he'd just have water.</i></font>

175
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he'd never want to play 
the crane catchers at the arcade.</i></font>

176
00:09:18,450 --> 00:09:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

177
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

178
00:09:21,450 --> 00:09:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to catch big plushies 
with him and stuff!</i></font>

179
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And stuff! And stuff! And stuff!</i></font>

180
00:09:30,490 --> 00:09:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No...</i></font>

181
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't be getting too excited.</i></font>

182
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's still Wednesday.</i></font>

183
00:09:37,060 --> 00:09:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Asking me out on a date is like 
walking willingly into my trap.</i></font>

184
00:09:42,610 --> 00:09:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm gonna be all set for Sunday 
and catch him off guard!</i></font>

185
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We live across from each other.</i></font>

186
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why are we meeting up at the station?</i></font>

187
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya!</font>

188
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I keep you waiting?</font>

189
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're here early.</font>

190
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TICKETS</font>

191
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

192
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just got here.</font>

193
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Really?</font>

194
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Err, what's with 
that saucy voice just now?</i></font>

195
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going dressed like <i>that</i>?</font>

196
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

197
00:10:48,650 --> 00:10:50,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What did he just say to me?</i></font>

198
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I spent three days and nights mulling 
this over and three hours preparing today!</i></font>

199
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did he just say "dressed like <i>that</i>"?</i></font>

200
00:10:59,260 --> 00:11:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me for a sec.</font>

201
00:11:00,970 --> 00:11:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Wait, Yukiya!</font>

202
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SCUTTLE - SO FAST</font>

203
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's so fast.</font>

204
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umm...</font>

205
00:11:10,820 --> 00:11:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a reservation under Asagi.</font>

206
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, we've been waiting for you.</font>

207
00:11:15,570 --> 00:11:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This lady here, correct?</font>

208
00:11:17,530 --> 00:11:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way, please.</font>

209
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FOR A SPECIAL CINDERELLA DAY</font>

210
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She came totally dressed up.</i></font>

211
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I really have had her get changed?</i></font>

212
00:11:30,050 --> 00:11:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, I planned this date 
based on this shoujo manga!</i></font>

213
00:11:33,810 --> 00:11:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to make it happen!</i></font>

214
00:11:35,730 --> 00:11:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can mess things up real bad 
if you don't follow the instructions</i></font>

215
00:11:38,130 --> 00:11:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>when you're building a PC, too.</i></font>

216
00:11:39,410 --> 00:11:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Trust in Hinako-san and the shoujo 
manga filled with a girls' dreams!</i></font>

217
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MONEY - INVESTMENTS</font>

218
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why is he making me get 
changed right off the bat?</i></font>

219
00:11:48,650 --> 00:11:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is my outfit really that bad?</i></font>

220
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're on a date?</font>

221
00:11:54,450 --> 00:11:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were attending a wedding.</font>

222
00:11:57,360 --> 00:12:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I haven't heard anything about this.</font>

223
00:12:00,450 --> 00:12:03,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's got to be difficult, huh?</font>

224
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you like to do?</font>

225
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to discuss it with him?</font>

226
00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Umm...</font>

227
00:12:08,370 --> 00:12:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think he wanted to surprise you.</font>

228
00:12:11,650 --> 00:12:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I answered his reservation call.</font>

229
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sounded terribly nervous.</font>

230
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was trying his best to tell me 
which dress he picked out.</font>

231
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yukiya picked this dress out for me?</i></font>

232
00:12:26,810 --> 00:12:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this the kind of dress he likes?</i></font>

233
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did he choose it because he 
thought it'd look good on me?</i></font>

234
00:12:35,590 --> 00:12:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll... take this one.</font>

235
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is the kind of thing 
you wanted me to wear, huh?</font>

236
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Happy?</font>

237
00:12:58,970 --> 00:13:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I SEE. - MM-HM.</font>

238
00:12:59,990 --> 00:13:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So joyful that you're 
at a loss for words?</font>

239
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They sure know how to make 
clothes that look good on anyone.</font>

240
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

241
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

242
00:13:08,730 --> 00:13:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go.</font>

243
00:13:10,850 --> 00:13:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

244
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

245
00:13:12,690 --> 00:13:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SLOW DOWN!</font>

246
00:13:13,490 --> 00:13:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Slow down!</font>

247
00:13:14,110 --> 00:13:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SCUTTLE</font>

248
00:13:19,290 --> 00:13:23,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The appetizer: 
salmon mi-cuit with dressing.</font>

249
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:31,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they high schoolers?</font>

250
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yukiya, are you sure about this?</font>

251
00:13:34,810 --> 00:13:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place looks expensive.</font>

252
00:13:37,650 --> 00:13:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see now?</font>

253
00:13:39,870 --> 00:13:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The subject of a grammable scene 
is meant to be the person</font>

254
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for whom such a venue and cuisine is apt.</font>

255
00:13:47,220 --> 00:13:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're dazzling right now.</font>

256
00:13:50,990 --> 00:13:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, wait, wait, 
we <i>really</i> stand out here!</font>

257
00:13:54,250 --> 00:13:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're out of place!</font>

258
00:13:57,630 --> 00:14:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who cares what anyone else thinks?</font>

259
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind that.</font>

260
00:14:03,590 --> 00:14:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just keep your eyes on me.</font>

261
00:14:06,370 --> 00:14:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

262
00:14:07,410 --> 00:14:08,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For sure.</font>

263
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For sure what?</font>

264
00:14:11,220 --> 00:14:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everyone else is a grown-up!</i></font>

265
00:14:14,050 --> 00:14:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so nervous being here!</i></font>

266
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Never mind the game!</i></font>

267
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good.</font>

268
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never had anything like this.</font>

269
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah?</font>

270
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's off the mark,</i></font>

271
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I can tell he's trying 
his best to impress me.</i></font>

272
00:14:40,290 --> 00:14:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's going all-out.</i></font>

273
00:14:43,710 --> 00:14:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems you're too distracted 
to even speak now.</font>

274
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what this date is for, don't you?</font>

275
00:14:52,380 --> 00:14:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just getting started!</font>

276
00:14:56,790 --> 00:15:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What is he going to mess up next?!</i></font>

277
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:05,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

278
00:15:05,260 --> 00:15:07,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the most appropriate 
decision yet today.</i></font>

279
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I like it!</i></font>

280
00:15:10,250 --> 00:15:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm at Wonderland with Yukiya!</i></font>

281
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:14,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we ride first?</font>

282
00:15:14,820 --> 00:15:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't decide.</font>

283
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:20,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Yukiya?</font>

284
00:15:20,110 --> 00:15:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

285
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thanks.</font>

286
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you feel anxious all on your own?</font>

287
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was worried you might have gotten lost!</font>

288
00:15:42,590 --> 00:15:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That line was so long, but it was so fun.</font>

289
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THIS IS ANOTHER COST</font>

290
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The ride ended instantly, 
and we waited a whole 120 minutes.</i></font>

291
00:15:49,050 --> 00:15:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My legs are getting pretty tired, though.</font>

292
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya, could I borrow your shoulder?</font>

293
00:15:57,980 --> 00:16:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, huh? What?!</font>

294
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, err...</font>

295
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd carry you if you're tired.</font>

296
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'know, like this.</font>

297
00:16:08,410 --> 00:16:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or are you too shy to take my offer?</font>

298
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:14,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it with the hands, you pervert!</font>

299
00:16:14,490 --> 00:16:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would I let you carry me here?!</font>

300
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like...</i></font>

301
00:16:22,170 --> 00:16:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He just keeps pulling weird acts.</i></font>

302
00:16:24,490 --> 00:16:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I feel like he's kinda pushing me.</i></font>

303
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miku.</font>

304
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to get him back next!</i></font>

305
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miku! Miku!</font>

306
00:16:35,110 --> 00:16:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you feel anything?</font>

307
00:16:39,160 --> 00:16:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go!</font>

308
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dunno!</font>

309
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at my profile 
shining in the nightscape.</font>

310
00:16:52,050 --> 00:16:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't I look good?</font>

311
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?!</font>

312
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you asking me if you 
made my heart skip a beat?</font>

313
00:16:57,010 --> 00:16:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heck if I know!</font>

314
00:17:02,900 --> 00:17:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, though, what's up with that?</font>

315
00:17:15,650 --> 00:17:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, come on.</i></font>

316
00:17:16,780 --> 00:17:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It </i>does<i> work.</i></font>

317
00:17:18,950 --> 00:17:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

318
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:23,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you still have more shenanigans?</font>

319
00:17:28,110 --> 00:17:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

320
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you close your eyes?</font>

321
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

322
00:17:35,850 --> 00:17:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, are we actually doing this?</font>

323
00:17:37,570 --> 00:17:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just close your eyes.</font>

324
00:18:00,140 --> 00:18:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just for tonight...</font>

325
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my very own princess.</font>

326
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, wait, wait!</font>

327
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is too cringe!</font>

328
00:18:10,460 --> 00:18:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what, do you have 
feelings for me now, then?</font>

329
00:18:13,970 --> 00:18:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

330
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not those kinds of feelings!</font>

331
00:18:16,450 --> 00:18:18,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax.</font>

332
00:18:18,230 --> 00:18:19,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one else is around.</font>

333
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just accept it and be happy.</font>

334
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, Yukiya...</font>

335
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're honestly pretty sketchy today.</font>

336
00:18:29,210 --> 00:18:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, yeah...</font>

337
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did feel pretty sketchy.</font>

338
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you did.</font>

339
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

340
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It left an impact on you, didn't it?</font>

341
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt you'll forget such a sketchy date.</font>

342
00:18:44,530 --> 00:18:50,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll never find another guy who 
gives you a tiara in front of a castle.</font>

343
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not...</font>

344
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting anyone else 
have your first.</font>

345
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya?</font>

346
00:19:17,250 --> 00:19:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya!</font>

347
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is going too far, 
even if no one's watching!</font>

348
00:19:24,020 --> 00:19:25,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya?</font>

349
00:19:25,970 --> 00:19:28,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya, are you okay?</font>

350
00:19:28,090 --> 00:19:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukiya?!</font>

351
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you embarrassed doing this?</font>

352
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're one to talk.</font>

353
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, are you really okay?</font>

354
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we go to the nurse's office?</font>

355
00:19:46,190 --> 00:19:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

356
00:19:47,510 --> 00:19:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just sleep deprived.</font>

357
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just need some time to rest.</font>

358
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sleep deprived?</font>

359
00:19:53,030 --> 00:19:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it,</font>

360
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your lights were on until late 
last night and the night before.</font>

361
00:19:57,850 --> 00:20:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were gaming again, weren't you?</font>

362
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LEAVE A GOOD IMPRESSION ON YOUR DATE!</font>

363
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}WHAT TO WATCH FOR IN YOUR OUTFIT</font>

364
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:01,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess.</font>

365
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it.</font>

366
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't be staying up so late 
before you're going out.</font>

367
00:20:06,890 --> 00:20:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then you went way out of 
your comfort zone today.</font>

368
00:20:09,410 --> 00:20:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No wonder you're exhausted.</font>

369
00:20:11,300 --> 00:20:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd normally refuse to wait 
in line at an amusement park.</font>

370
00:20:15,710 --> 00:20:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you'd never waste money 
on an expensive lunch or tiara.</font>

371
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't need to push yourself so much.</font>

372
00:20:35,710 --> 00:20:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}HOT SPRING LOOKS FOR MEN
KOI-KYUN</font>

373
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have to.</font>

374
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yukiya...</font>

375
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

376
00:21:12,450 --> 00:21:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I stun you?</font>

377
00:21:18,610 --> 00:21:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

378
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:23,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had tons of fun today.</font>

379
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, I never stood a chance.</i></font>

380
00:21:29,590 --> 00:21:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She acts so childish all the time.</i></font>

381
00:21:32,300 --> 00:21:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then she shows off her grown-up side.</i></font>

382
00:21:35,390 --> 00:21:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I tried so hard to beat her.</i></font>

383
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to push yourself so much.</font>

384
00:21:43,110 --> 00:21:44,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

385
00:21:46,890 --> 00:21:48,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm nowhere near her level.</i></font>

386
00:21:51,990 --> 00:21:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna go buy something to drink.</font>

387
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That startled me!</i></font>

388
00:22:04,210 --> 00:22:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never expected that surprise attack.</i></font>

389
00:22:07,530 --> 00:22:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It seemed like something 
was weighing on him.</i></font>

390
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting anyone else 
have your first.</font>

391
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What was that supposed to mean?</i></font>

392
00:22:27,910 --> 00:22:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NO, I JUST GOT HERE.</font>

393
00:22:29,490 --> 00:22:30,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}WH-WHAT?</font>

394
00:22:30,870 --> 00:22:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ARE YOU GOING DRESSED LIKE <i>THAT</i>?</font>

395
00:22:33,510 --> 00:22:34,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}COME WITH ME FOR A SEC.</font>

396
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is why!</font>

397
00:22:38,210 --> 00:22:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is why Yukiya was being so weird!</font>

398
00:22:40,710 --> 00:22:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This one's full of sticky notes, too.</i></font>

399
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's been reading like crazy.</i></font>

400
00:22:45,890 --> 00:22:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just sleep deprived.</font>

401
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's such a goof.</i></font>

402
00:22:50,450 --> 00:22:52,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He took it so far.</i></font>

403
00:22:52,300 --> 00:22:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Went out of character.</i></font>

404
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:58,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He must have been super embarrassed, too.</i></font>

405
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's </i>that<i> desperate to win against me?</i></font>

406
00:23:03,650 --> 00:23:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why is he trying so hard to win?</i></font>

407
00:23:15,210 --> 00:23:17,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I... CAN'T HOLD BACK ANYMORE.</font>

408
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? Wait.</i></font>

409
00:23:21,130 --> 00:23:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this...</i></font>

410
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A kiss?</i></font>

411
00:23:24,130 --> 00:23:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A kiss?</i></font>

412
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A kiss?!</i></font>

413
00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED</font>

414
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MY CHILDHOOD FRIEND WILL DO ANYTHING</font>

415
00:23:30,630 --> 00:23:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the coffee shop from Seattle 
with the childhood friend!</font>

416
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the library with the childhood friend!</font>

417
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In front of the janitor room 
with the childhood friend!</font>

418
00:23:36,100 --> 00:23:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And at the common stairs!</font>

419
00:23:37,810 --> 00:23:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on...</font>

420
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh, Onii! You've got 
everything you could want!</font>

421
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:42,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next episode: "My Childhood 
Friend Will Do Anything!"</font>

422
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you there!</font>

